<P>A clicky heal on the same timer as Tacvi hammer is the best idea in this thread imo.&nbsp; Direwood guard would be nice too, especially if the timer has to stay at 15 mins.&nbsp; GoRM would be nice as well,&nbsp;with a lower recast timer though.&nbsp; I would even be happy with a clicky nuke assuming the recast delay was much lower.</P>
