<P>We can ask for a clicky nuke or dot, but would kinda defeat the purpose.&nbsp; Look at the DS right now as a free nuke....it does mana free damage, just as a ds and not a direct damage as you would cast the DS on the tank...much like the Wrath of Wild AA.&nbsp; As well, a DS is not resistable, a nuke and dot are.&nbsp; I am not too concerned about the DS clicky on the BP, while it is not my first choice, I can live with it.&nbsp; </P>
